attributes.Long form description: The first instruction is to assemble the furniture. The student inspects the furniture and proceeds to align the furniture legs but the instructor corrects the student and indicates how to align the legs. Finally, the student crosses the furniture legs and screws the top legs table with the allen wrench, then screws the bottom legs table. Next, the student places the circle on the top of the table and screws it. The last instruction is to place the tray over the legs.
